[Civil No. 785.] JUAN ESPINOSO, Appellant, v. QUILINO ESPINOSO, Appellee. W. Y. PRICE, Defendant. APPEAL from the District Court of the Second Judicial District in and for the County of Pinal. F. M. Doan, Judge. Jesse Hardesty, Attorney for Appellant. W. H. Griffin, and Owen T. Rouse, Attorneys for Appellee. October 31, 1902.

Dismissed.
